stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> starting: registerDreamTask\n（phase=starting）
    starting --> updating: addDreamTurn\n收到首个 Edit/Write 工具调用
    starting --> starting: addDreamTurn\n纯文本响应（无工具调用）
    updating --> updating: addDreamTurn\n继续整理
    starting --> completed: completeDreamTask
    updating --> completed: completeDreamTask\n（notified=true）
    starting --> failed: failDreamTask
    updating --> failed: failDreamTask
    starting --> killed: DreamTask.kill\n+ rollbackConsolidationLock
    updating --> killed: DreamTask.kill\n+ rollbackConsolidationLock
    completed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期
    failed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期
    killed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期
